{
  "stem": "21004.8",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we have to go to another place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had to cross.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Soon, we cross that road, that expressway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Two cars are coming with the lights.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Coming closer.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We jumped in on the other side of the road.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a little threes there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We hide in those trees.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And just when they came by us, the two cars stopped.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Two limousines stop.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was gestapo.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was German gestapo.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they stop just in the front on the highway, and we are on the other side deeper in little-- little woods.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We couldn't breathe, nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We thought that maybe they saw us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they didn't saw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They just had a flat tired.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But you know, it took them an hour till they finished there to put in the flat tire, till they stretch themselves, and all of that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And meanwhile, we were scared to death and sitting, not a move.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We didn't have nothing to shoot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We-- if you have, you know, a rifle or whatever, you could shoot them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There were three in one car, three gestapo in the other car.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But anyway, to start something like this, it's already a search for somebody who kill gestapo.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The best way we figured out not to kill nobody, not to have anything involved, you know, that somebody should look in exactly for us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we were very careful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- later they moved away and they gone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went our way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we got-- now, the other thing is when I went to the gentleman where I build the bunker, and I had to go with all the food, everything on our shoulders, to carry everything, me and the boy.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were going, and we couldn't go through.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
